OL,5,G0100 Outback Truckers
OL,6,     FJustin Harrison is going downhill
OL,7,     Ffast when his gearbox fails, and
OL,8,     Fcows play chicken with Sonny
OL,9,     FForrest's monster road train.
OL,10,G0200 Trucking Hell
OL,11,     FA 44-tonne gravel lorry careers
OL,12,     Foff the A697, plunging down an
OL,13,     Fembankment, and Gary must pick up
OL,14,     Fthe pieces. In Croydon, Stu has a
OL,15,     Fcomplex recovery: a bin lorry is
OL,16,     Fstuck in deep mud.
